data.description: Welcome to 821 N. 2nd St, a 4-bed, 2-bath home in the Centre Park Historic District, Reading, PA. This charming property seamlessly blends modern comforts with classic character. The spacious living room features original hardwood floors and ample natural light, flowing into the dining area. The updated kitchen boasts white appliances, gas cooking, and generous cabinet space. Upstairs, four well-appointed bedrooms cater to your storage needs, accompanied by two full bathrooms. The partially finished basement offers a versatile space with a laundry area and a pool table for indoor entertainment. The fenced backyard and covered porch create a private oasis for relaxation or outdoor entertaining. Conveniently located within the historic district, this home provides easy access to schools, parks, shopping, dining, and transportation routes. Embrace the rich history and architectural beauty while enjoying the convenience of city living. With thoughtful updates and a prestigious location, 821 N. 2nd St is an excellent opportunity in the Reading real estate market. Contact me to schedule a private showing and discover all that this home has to offer.
